	<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">昆山开发区经促局、昆山高新区、花桥经济开发区经发局，各镇招商服务中心，各有关企业：</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">为加快发展壮大实体经济，突出创新驱动，充分发挥标杆企业的引领作用，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>9</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月份我委组织举办了</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">昆山走进深圳</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>—</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">标杆企业创新体验式特训班</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，参训企业反响热烈。根据企业要求，并经研究决定，我委将组织第二期深圳培训班，具体通知如下：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">一、培训时间：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>11</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月份工作日，往返共</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>5</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">天时间。具体开班时间另行通知。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">二、培训内容：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">采取参观</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>+</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">学习</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>+</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">交流为形式，考察学习华为、中兴通讯、创维集团及腾讯集团，举办《传统企业战略转型与落地策略》讲座。方案见附件</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">三、参加对象：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">实体企业董事长、总经理等中高层管理者组成的学习团队。由企业高管带队，每家报名人数原则上不超过</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">人，每期班总人数</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>50</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">人。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5.25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: .5gd" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">四、培训费用：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">培训费用由市财政提供全额补贴，统一安排食宿。学员按</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1000</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">元</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>/</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">人交纳住宿费，至深圳往返机票交通费由企业自理。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5.25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: .5gd" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">为保障报名学员的出勤率和作业的完成率，每人缴纳</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1000</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">元学习保证金至培训承办机构，待完成学业后退还。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5.25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: .5gd" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">五、报名方式：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">请区镇组织科技小巨人培育企业和制造业骨干企业报名参加，开发区、高新区、张浦、周市、巴城区镇推荐企业不少于</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家，其他不少于</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家。上次符合条件但未录取的学员本次培训优先参加。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5.25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: .5gd" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">请企业填写报名表，由区镇汇总后发送至指定邮箱，经过市经信委审核录取后，通知企业缴费、行程安排等事宜。报名截止时间为</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>10</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>13</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">日。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5.25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-left: .5gd" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">市经信委联系人：张柏林</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">周晨</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">电话：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>57556650<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
